data.description:
A charming 4 bed, 2 bath residence in the heart of Phoenix is now for sale! Sitting right in front of a Park this home Features charming curb appeal, easy-care landscape, and RV parking, with a Gate Big enough to convert to a Large RV Gate. This is sure to be the home you've been looking for! Inside you'll find a spacious open floor plan w/elegant wood-look tile flooring, modern light fixtures, and neutral palette throughout. The fabulous kitchen is equipped w/everything you need for home cooking, white cabinetry, quartz counters, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, and a peninsula complete w/a breakfast bar. The primary bedroom boasts an ample closet and private bath for added comfort. 
 What are you waiting for? Act now!
